des: Boom Station SLU is a St. Lucian radio station tagging along with the Boom family in New York. We create the party atmosphere by playing the hottest music from St. Lucia and the Caribbean. Dancehall, Reggae and Soca just to name a few genres. We are streaming online 24/7 and you can also listen on 89.9 FM in St. Lucia. Our mission is education through entertainment. We have some of the best interactive DJS and announcers, for the latest in news, Sports, interviews, educational programmes and more, Boom station SLU is your # 1 choice.
